HEADWORD: Blue-eyed grass
<hw>Blue-eyed grass</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>a
grasslike plant (<spn>Sisyrinchium anceps</spn>), with small flowers of
a delicate blue color.</def>⟦br⟧
